<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n38080e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38080e">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38080e"> 80(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 1 guest / 20 hosts</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Tayish]</font> suddenly sat up, raised his hand and cried: &ldquo;Here is a riddle for you. <mark>Twenty hosts and one guest</mark>. Who is it?&rdquo; <br>&ldquo;I have guessed it,&rdquo; said the man from Ashdod&mdash;he was older than the rest and had not yet drunk so freely&mdash;&ldquo;Our host pays for the revels with the money he has won from us at play.&rdquo; <small> Vladimir Jabotinsky, <a name="VEJS" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#VEJS"><cite title="source">Samson the Nazarite</cite></a>,(Jan 1930) 16</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
